The '''Yawari Cliffs''' were a geographical feature on the [[Endor/Legends|Forest Moon]] of [[Endor (planet)/Legends|Endor]]. The cliffs resembled a plateau, separating the lower more lush and forested [[Jiberah Plains]] and [[Mertuen Forest]] to the south, and the higher more barren [[Desert of Salma/Legends|Desert of Salma]] to the north.<ref name="SWG">{{GalaxiesAED}}</ref>

{{Nature-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
The Yawari Cliffs were one of many designated planetary regions in the [[2003]] [[Star Wars video games|video game]] ''[[Star Wars Galaxies]]'', a [[Wikipedia:Massively multiplayer online role-playing game|massively multiplayer online roleplaying game]] developed by [[Sony]] Online Entertainment and published by [[LucasArts]],<ref name="SWG" /> prior to its closure on [[December 15]], [[2011]].<ref name="Shutdown">{{SonyCite|url=playerinfo|text=IMPORTANT INFORMATION ABOUT ''STAR WARS'' GALAXIES™}}</ref>

